        <h2>About Amateur Radio Weekly</h2>
        <p>Our objective at Amateur Radio Weekly is to help promote Amateur Radio both as a hobby and as a community resource by highlighting and sharing the most exceptional Ham Radio content on the web. We're most interested in promoting the latest cutting-edge ideas, technology, and methods found in the hobby today. <a href="about/">Learn more about Amateur Radio Weekly</a>.</p>
        <p>If you have a project or something else you think the world of Ham Radio should know about, <a href="mailto:k4hck@hamweekly.com">send it to us</a>. We're always on the lookout for good content to share in our weekly newsletter.</p>
